{"article_id":"CiNiP8B7T17pFfnM","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"WASHINGTON -","depth":1},{"id":1,"text":"President Donald Trump repeatedly pressed the president of Ukraine to reopen an investigation into a Ukrainian energy company","depth":8},{"id":2,"text":"to focus on Democratic presidential candidate Joe Biden and his son Hunter ,","depth":8},{"id":3,"text":"according to a summary of a telephone call July 25 between the two leaders .","depth":7},{"id":4,"text":"In the 30-minute call ,","depth":9},{"id":5,"text":"recounted in a five-page memo","depth":10},{"id":6,"text":"released by the administration Wednesday ,","depth":10},{"id":7,"text":"Trump told President Volodymyr Zelensky","depth":9},{"id":8,"text":"that he was directing his personal attorney Rudy Giuliani and Attorney General William Barr to assist in the inquiry","depth":10},{"id":9,"text":"\" to get to the bottom of it . \"","depth":10},{"id":10,"text":"Trump told Zelensky","depth":9},{"id":11,"text":"there was `` a lot of talk '' about Biden 's son 's activities in Ukraine .","depth":9},{"id":12,"text":"`` A lot of people want to find out about that","depth":9},{"id":13,"text":"so whatever you can do with the attorney general would be great , \"","depth":10},{"id":14,"text":"Trump said .","depth":10},{"id":15,"text":"The memo was released","depth":6},{"id":16,"text":"the day after House Speaker Nancy Pelosi announced an impeachment inquiry .","depth":6},{"id":17,"text":"Trump first acknowledged bringing up Biden in the Zelensky phone call Sunday .","depth":7},{"id":18,"text":"Democrats said","depth":11},{"id":19,"text":"asking a foreign government to investigate a political rival is an egregious abuse of power .","depth":11},{"id":20,"text":"They questioned","depth":11},{"id":21,"text":"whether Trump used congressionally approved military aid","depth":13},{"id":22,"text":"intended for Ukraine","depth":13},{"id":23,"text":"as leverage","depth":13},{"id":24,"text":"to push for an investigation of Biden .","depth":13},{"id":25,"text":"Trump insisted","depth":10},{"id":26,"text":"there was no pressure nor any `` quid pro quo . ''","depth":10},{"id":27,"text":"Impeachment inquiry :","depth":9},{"id":28,"text":"'No one is above the law ' :","depth":10},{"id":29,"text":"Pelosi announces inquiry","depth":10},{"id":30,"text":"Trump referred to Barr at least four times during the call ,","depth":9},{"id":31,"text":"suggesting","depth":10},{"id":32,"text":"the attorney general and Giuliani could help restart an inquiry into Burisma , a gas company","depth":11},{"id":33,"text":"where Hunter Biden served on the board in 2014","depth":12},{"id":34,"text":"while his father , as Barack Obama 's vice president , worked closely with the Ukrainian government .","depth":12},{"id":35,"text":"The Obama White House denied","depth":9},{"id":36,"text":"that there was any conflict of interest .","depth":9},{"id":37,"text":"Trump told Zelensky of the Biden matter :","depth":8},{"id":38,"text":"`` If you can look into it ...","depth":9},{"id":39,"text":"it sounds horrible to me . ''","depth":9},{"id":40,"text":"Officials said","depth":6},{"id":41,"text":"ellipses were used","depth":7},{"id":42,"text":"when the conversation was inaudible","depth":8},{"id":43,"text":"and not picked up by voice recognition software .","depth":8},{"id":44,"text":"It is the first time","depth":4},{"id":45,"text":"another administration official has emerged in Trump ' s effort","depth":5},{"id":46,"text":"to a solicit a foreign power ' s help","depth":6},{"id":47,"text":"in investigating a political rival .","depth":6},{"id":48,"text":"Despite the repeated references to Barr in Trump ' s call ,","depth":5},{"id":49,"text":"Justice Department spokeswoman Kerri Kupec said","depth":6},{"id":50,"text":"that the attorney general learned of the president ' s conversation \" several weeks \" after it took place","depth":7},{"id":51,"text":"and that Barr has not communicated with Ukrainian officials .","depth":7},{"id":52,"text":"Justice officials acknowledged Wednesday","depth":9},{"id":53,"text":"that the intelligence community ' s inspector general referred Trump ' s call to the Justice Department and the FBI for possible criminal investigation","depth":11},{"id":54,"text":"related to a possible violation of campaign finance law","depth":11},{"id":55,"text":"after the president ' s contact with Ukraine became the subject of a whistleblower ' s complaint last month .","depth":10},{"id":56,"text":"Read the transcript :","depth":9},{"id":57,"text":"President Trump 's call with Ukraine president about Biden","depth":9},{"id":58,"text":"\" The inspector general ' s letter cited a conversation between the president and Ukrainian President Zelensky as a potential violation of federal campaign finance law , \"","depth":10},{"id":59,"text":"Kupec said .","depth":10},{"id":60,"text":"\" Relying on established procedures","depth":11},{"id":61,"text":"set forth ...","depth":11},{"id":62,"text":"the department ' s Criminal Division reviewed the official record of the call","depth":11},{"id":63,"text":"and determined ,","depth":13},{"id":64,"text":"based on the facts and applicable law ,","depth":13},{"id":65,"text":"that there was no campaign finance violation","depth":13},{"id":66,"text":"and no further action was warranted . \"","depth":13},{"id":67,"text":"Justice officials said","depth":11},{"id":68,"text":"Barr was aware of the inspector general ' s referral","depth":12},{"id":69,"text":"but did not make the final decision to reject the opening of a criminal investigation of the president .","depth":12},{"id":70,"text":"The officials acknowledged","depth":11},{"id":71,"text":"that the Justice Department review did not include interviews of potential witnesses to Trump ' s call or others with potential knowledge of it .","depth":11},{"id":72,"text":"\" All relevant components of the department agreed with these legal conclusions ,","depth":11},{"id":73,"text":"and the department has concluded the matter , \"","depth":11},{"id":74,"text":"Kupec said .","depth":10},{"id":75,"text":"The decision not to open a criminal investigation","depth":8},{"id":76,"text":"was made last week ,","depth":8},{"id":77,"text":"Justice officials said .","depth":7},{"id":78,"text":"Trump seemed eager to offer Barr ' s help to Zelensky on both the Burisma inquiry and another longtime obsession of the president ' s :","depth":8},{"id":79,"text":"missing emails and the hack of a computer server at the Democratic National Committee .","depth":8},{"id":80,"text":"\" The server ,","depth":10},{"id":81,"text":"they say","depth":11},{"id":82,"text":"Ukraine has it , \"","depth":11},{"id":83,"text":"Trump told his counterpart .","depth":9},{"id":84,"text":"\" There are a lot of things","depth":10},{"id":85,"text":"that went on , the whole situation . ...","depth":10},{"id":86,"text":"I would like to have the attorney general call you or your people","depth":10},{"id":87,"text":"and I would like you to get to the bottom of it . \"","depth":10},{"id":88,"text":"Justice officials maintained Wednesday","depth":8},{"id":89,"text":"that the attorney general had not spoken with the president about Trump ' s interest","depth":9},{"id":90,"text":"in targeting Biden or his son .","depth":9},{"id":91,"text":"`` The president has not asked the attorney general to contact Ukraine","depth":10},{"id":92,"text":"- on this or any other matter , \"","depth":10},{"id":93,"text":"Kupec said .","depth":9},{"id":94,"text":"\" The attorney general has not communicated with Ukraine","depth":10},{"id":95,"text":"- on this or any other subject .","depth":10},{"id":96,"text":"Nor has the attorney general discussed this matter ,","depth":11},{"id":97,"text":"or anything","depth":12},{"id":98,"text":"related to Ukraine ,","depth":12},{"id":99,"text":"with Rudy Giuliani . \"","depth":10},{"id":100,"text":"Hillary Clinton , Trump 's opponent in the 2016 election , called for his impeachment shortly after the release .","depth":5},{"id":101,"text":"`` The president of the United States has betrayed our country , ''","depth":8},{"id":102,"text":"she tweeted .","depth":8},{"id":103,"text":"`` That ' s not a political statement","depth":9},{"id":104,"text":"- it ' s a harsh reality ,","depth":10},{"id":105,"text":"and we must act .","depth":10},{"id":106,"text":"He is a clear and present danger to the things","depth":9},{"id":107,"text":"that keep us strong and free .","depth":9},{"id":108,"text":"I support impeachment . ''","depth":6},{"id":109,"text":"The chairman of the House Intelligence Committee , Rep. Adam Schiff , D-Calif. , tweeted","depth":7},{"id":110,"text":"that the call sounded like a shakedown for favors","depth":8},{"id":111,"text":"in exchange","depth":9},{"id":112,"text":"for investigating Trump 's opponents .","depth":9},{"id":113,"text":"`` The transcript of the call reads like a classic mob shakedown , ''","depth":7},{"id":114,"text":"Schiff said .","depth":7},{"id":115,"text":"Trump ,","depth":12},{"id":116,"text":"who described the investigation in a tweet as the `` most Destructive Witch Hunt of all time , ''","depth":12},{"id":117,"text":"demanded an apology from Democrats","depth":11},{"id":118,"text":"after the transcript was released .","depth":10},{"id":119,"text":"\" The way","depth":14},{"id":120,"text":"you had that built up ,","depth":14},{"id":121,"text":"that call was going to be the call from hell , ''","depth":13},{"id":122,"text":"Trump told reporters Wednesday at the United Nations in New York .","depth":12},{"id":123,"text":"\" It turned out to be a nothing call . \"","depth":11},{"id":124,"text":"Trump argued","depth":11},{"id":125,"text":"that the transcript did not demonstrate","depth":12},{"id":126,"text":"that he leaned on Ukraine","depth":13},{"id":127,"text":"to open an investigation into Biden .","depth":13},{"id":128,"text":"Trump remained in New York on Wednesday for the U.N. General Assembly","depth":9},{"id":129,"text":"- and one of his meetings was with Ukrainian President Zelensky .","depth":9},{"id":130,"text":"The Aug. 12 whistleblower complaint arrived on Capitol Hill Wednesday .","depth":8},{"id":131,"text":"Thursday , the acting director of national security is scheduled to appear before lawmakers .","depth":10},{"id":132,"text":"Schiff said","depth":11},{"id":133,"text":"the whistleblower asked to speak with the Intelligence Committee ,","depth":12},{"id":134,"text":"and attorneys are negotiating the ground rules for such an appearance .","depth":12},{"id":135,"text":"`` We ' re in touch with counsel","depth":11},{"id":136,"text":"and look forward to the whistleblower ' s testimony as soon as this week , ''","depth":11},{"id":137,"text":"Schiff tweeted .","depth":10},{"id":138,"text":"What 's changed :","depth":8},{"id":139,"text":"Here 's what led to Pelosi 's call for an impeachment inquiry","depth":8},{"id":140,"text":"Some legal analysts said","depth":11},{"id":141,"text":"Trump 's casual talk about assistance to Ukraine in a conversation","depth":13},{"id":142,"text":"that touched on investigating Biden","depth":13},{"id":143,"text":"looks like bribery .","depth":12},{"id":144,"text":"`` Even as summarized by this White House , and what we know about the freeze on Ukraine aid before the call ,","depth":13},{"id":145,"text":"any competent federal prosecutor would charge this as a quid pro quo , ''","depth":13},{"id":146,"text":"said Mimi Rocah , a former federal prosecutor in New York .","depth":12},{"id":147,"text":"`` This is bribery . ''","depth":11},{"id":148,"text":"Acknowledging","depth":11},{"id":149,"text":"he discussed Biden on the call ,","depth":11},{"id":150,"text":"Trump said","depth":11},{"id":151,"text":"he only wanted to make sure","depth":12},{"id":152,"text":"Ukraine was thoroughly investigating claims of corruption .","depth":12},{"id":153,"text":"Trump said","depth":10},{"id":154,"text":"he held up U.S. assistance to Ukraine before his phone call with Zelensky","depth":11},{"id":155,"text":"because allies such as France and Germany were n't contributing enough foreign aid to the country .","depth":11},{"id":156,"text":"At the time","depth":12},{"id":157,"text":"Trump and Zelensky spoke ,","depth":12},{"id":158,"text":"the Trump administration was holding up hundreds of millions of dollars in military aid","depth":12},{"id":159,"text":"approved by Congress .","depth":12},{"id":160,"text":"The memo did not lay out a specific threat","depth":14},{"id":161,"text":"to withhold military aid ,","depth":14},{"id":162,"text":"but during the call , the president played up U.S. commitment to support Ukraine","depth":14},{"id":163,"text":"while bashing much of Europe .","depth":14},{"id":164,"text":"\" I will say","depth":14},{"id":165,"text":"that we do a lot for Ukraine , \"","depth":15},{"id":166,"text":"Trump said .","depth":15},{"id":167,"text":"\" We spend a lot of effort and a lot of time .","depth":15},{"id":168,"text":"Much more","depth":17},{"id":169,"text":"than the European countries are doing","depth":17},{"id":170,"text":"and they should be helping you more","depth":17},{"id":171,"text":"than they are .","depth":17},{"id":172,"text":"Germany does almost nothing for you . \"","depth":14},{"id":173,"text":"Zelensky assured Trump","depth":13},{"id":174,"text":"that a prosecutor would look into the Burisma matter","depth":13},{"id":175,"text":"and broached the country ' s need for defense assistance .","depth":13},{"id":176,"text":"\" I would also like to thank you for your great support in the area of defense , \"","depth":15},{"id":177,"text":"Zelensky said .","depth":15},{"id":178,"text":"\" We are ready to continue to cooperate for the next steps ;","depth":15},{"id":179,"text":"specifically we are almost ready to buy more","depth":17},{"id":180,"text":"( anti-tank missiles )","depth":17},{"id":181,"text":"from the United States for defense purposes . \"","depth":16}],"relations":[{"parent":363,"left":0,"right":362,"r